				<pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2020 05:30:21 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Zyn</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1404533</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>How do I obtain Karma?</p> </blockquote> <p>Wikidot's explanation is here: <a href="http://www.wikidot.com/doc:karma">http://www.wikidot.com/doc:karma</a></p> <p>For the record, wikidot karma is essentially meaningless on the SCP wiki since it just tracks activity across all wikidot sites. For example, someone with dozens of sandbox drafts and nothing successful posted to the site would likely have more karma than an author of a page rated +100 but with few edits.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
